  "steps": [
    "Soak tamarind and extract thin juice; crush the tomato into it.",
    "Add rasam powder, turmeric, salt and crushed garlic, pepper and cumin.",
    "Simmer gently until frothy on top — do not boil hard.",
    "Make a ghee tadka of mustard, red chillies and curry leaves and pour over.",
    "Garnish with coriander; drink hot or mix with rice."
